name: CABG_Endoscopic_ICD10PCS
title: CABG_Endoscopic_ICD10PCS
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values identifies patients who have a CABG surgical procedure using endoscopic approach.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have a CABG surgical procedure using endoscopic approach.  Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the Procedure category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Only use codes which represent CABG surgical procedures using endoscopic approach.  Codes used are to be ICD10PCS codes only.),(Exclusion Criteria: Exclude codes that represent a CABG performed using open approach.)
